Package pt.ipp.isep.dei.g312.application.controller

Class RegisterCollaboratorController

java.lang.Object
pt.ipp.isep.dei.g312.application.controller.RegisterCollaboratorController
public class RegisterCollaboratorController extends Object
This class is responsible for handling collaborator registration functionalities. It interacts with repositories to register new employees and retrieve job information.
